RTM-GLib
========


Description
-----------

*RTM-GLib* is a library which provides access to the API of Remember The Milk.

Remember The Milk [1]_ is a task and time management web application.


Requirements
------------

*RTM-GLib* depens on:

* GLib (``glib-2.0``)
* librest (``rest``) [2]_


Installation
------------

See the ``INSTALL`` file.


Availability
------------

The cutting-edge version of this project is always available from the Git
repository at http://gitorious.org/rtm-glib/.


Webpage
-------

You can find more information about *RTM-GLib* at
http://live.gnome.org/RTMGlib/.


